{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he moved to Holland, the uncle, you know, who owned the business that my father was working in at the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was I think, '37.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't really notice anything until Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I just noticed that my father kept on losing his job and we couldn't-- couldn't find another job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had-- we couldn't afford to live where we had been living, because there was no money coming in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my lifestyle changed somewhat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's the only thing I noticed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not aware of any anti-Semitism-- What were--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--until '38 I would say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I-- then when we moved to Lipp-- to Bielefeld, my sister was in school then too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin-- this uncle that my father worked for-- she, her name is Lotte, and she was in school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the three of us were the only Jewish children in this one school in Bielefeld.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other Jews in Bielefeld.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it just happened that we were the only ones at that school, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not until-- there was no difference until '38.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- I never encountered any prejudice until Hit-- until Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that's what changed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We then moved into a house which we had to share with another Jewish family, because, you know, things were beginning to change.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father worked for an organization called [GERMAN] [GERMAN] [GERMAN] [GERMAN] which means like self help for Jewish-- for German Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was involved in getting help for people and also trying to get people out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why we didn't get out, but we didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was a-- I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a business job.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
